    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast gear changes, perfectly complemented by a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal torque vectoring. This example remains mechanically robust, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing service and refreshed throttle actuators. The chassis retains its composure via the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system, providing sharp turn-in and balanced lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and subframe integrity are excellent, making this a prime candidate for a dedicated driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
